    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am so excited to show you this absolute beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in such pristine condition that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered, garage-kept, and is looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. If you're looking for a ride that's basically flawless and ready for an adventure, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
