    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays in absolutely flawless shape. It drives like a total dream and looks even better. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, you've found it! Let's get you in the driver's seat today!",
      "price": 43500.0,
