      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This specimen features the S54B32 inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a stratospheric 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis integrity is superlative, with a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh utilizing OEM bushings to maintain factory-spec kinematics. Every mechanical system, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been scrutinized and maintained to peak performance standards. This is a turn-key example of the ultimate driving machine, free of common failure points and ready for the most rigorous enthusiast inspection.",
